sources.title: Great Guy (restored) (1936, film noir, imdb score: 6.3)
sources.description: Great Guy is a 1936 American crime film noir directed by John G. Blystone and starring James Cagney . In the film, an honest inspector for the New York Department of Weights and Measures takes on corrupt merchants and politicians.
